EmailTemplate.subject: Welcome to SunPower
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Contact.FirstName}:
Thank you for making the choice to partner with SunPower. We are excited to work with you through our SunPower Direct (SPD) Installation Partner Program.
One of the key tools we have to support your efforts is a SunPower Partner Portal that provides access to customer opportunities, design tools, Marketing Resource Center, SunPower University, data sheets, logos, and more.
As part of our 'On Boarding' process, we have provided you user access to the Partner Portal. Please complete the attached Vendor Enrollment Form and W9 Form (to ensure payment) and send to RACompliance@sunpowercorp.com. Also, please complete the attached IP Contacts list and send it to your assigned Installation Partner Manager (IPM) so that we can process partner portal access for these personnel.
In addition, while your Installation Partner Manager (IPM) is your primary contact with SunPower, please be aware that the email addresses below serve as excellent resources if you have questions that can potentially be easily answered via email. The support teams behind these email addresses have deep knowledge and respond quickly.
Partner Portal Management: partnerportal@sunpowercorp.com Training: trainingsupport@sunpowercorp.com
We look forward to doing business with you.
Sincerely,
Your SunPower Team
77 Rio Robles San Jose, CA 95134 Phone: 408.240.5580 Fax: 408.240.5400 www.sunpowercorp.com
